["IDf2a4de6af84897e0"] = "너희들 괜찮아? 폭주족놈들은 이게 무슨 전쟁인줄 아나보군 - 죽여버려!", --You guys OK? Bikers sure act like it is war - go get 'em!
["IDbe3658086d4199b2"] = "젠장! 저 녀석들이 파일들을 태우고 있어!", --Damn it, they're burning it!
["ID8de3076483f5bfbf"] = "이봐, 놈들이 정보를 또 없애고 있어!", --Guys they are fucking up more intel!
["ID3d0adb473e5a2a2c"] = "정보, 이 친구들아! 정보! 가져와!", --Intel guys, intel! Get it!
["IDe52e90c87081b55b"] = "전부 불지옥으로 만들고 있군 - 정보를 챙겨!", --It is all going to hell - get the intel!
["IDa4b2f1deb40f014b"] = "잘했어! 밴으로 가져와.", --Nice! Get it to the van.
["ID87ff28c79b9b2a77"] = "훌륭해! 밴으로 가방을 가져와.", --Sweet! Bring the bag to the van.
["ID6d82a4c4063915a0"] = "이런, 경찰들이 신고를 받은 게 분명해.", --Crap, the cops must have recieved a call.
["ID75d82c6b234818a7"] = "잠시 경찰들이 끼어드는일 없이 작업을 해보고 싶었는데 말이야.", --Was hoping we'd do this without police for once.
["ID7a8ec756a5f348c2"] = "좋아, 저기 있는 집 보여? 안으로 들어가. 카메라와 경비들을 조심하고.", --Alright, do you see the house? Get inside. Look out for guards and cameras.
["ID4e4bcd10a19904ef"] = "집은 나무 건너편에 있어, 보여? 조심히 들어가.", --House is beyond those trees, see? Sneak right up.
["IDedce798d074647a5"] = "집은 바로 건너편에 있고 숲 사이에 있어. 움직여.", --The house is right across and through the woods. Leg it. 
["ID821a56590fd962bc"] = "그리고... 알렉스가 요청한 탄약을 투하했을꺼야. 어딘가에 말이야.", --And... Alex made the requested drop. Somewhere.
["ID6522dc0e3803685a"] = "알렉스가 탄약을 어디에다 떨어트렸는지 확인해. 패닉룸 때가 생각나게 하는군...", --Check for Alex ammo drop... Panic room all over again...
["ID8ef8264b4d332df8"] = "알렉스... 그 멍청이가 탄약을 떨어 트렸어... 어디론가로.", --Alex... The idiot dropped the ammo... Elsewhere. 
["ID0e622e9ff0cc31c3"] = "알렉스가 잘 떨궜어, 그 녀석한테 세 번째 기회를 줘도 괜찮을 줄 알았다니까.", --Alex made the drop, I knew I was right in giving him a third chance.
["IDa027900699dc4e43"] = "명중이로군. 알렉스가 잘 떨궜어.", --Smack daddy in the middle. Alex dropped good.
["ID444293cc29ac6c28"] = "알렉스가 잘 해냈어. 탄약은 바로 저기에 있어.", --Alex nailed it. Ammo is right there.
["ID566ca1458a90f79b"] = "시제품들은 연구실에 있을거야. 안으로 들어가려면 주요 서버를 해킹해야해. 서버실을 찾아봐.", --The prototypes should be in the lab. To gain access to it we need to hack the main server. Find the server room.
["ID5a700aa5e8ad249d"] = "서버실을 찾아. 그곳에서 연구실 문을 열 수 있을꺼야.", --Find the server room. From there we should be able to open the lab door.
["ID950bbd00116cd603"] = "연구실은 놈들의 서버를 해킹해야 열릴꺼야. 서버실을 찾아.", --The lab we are after should open by hacking their server. Find the server room.
["ID6272a5e7ed48220f"] = "기억해. 너희들은 서버실을 찾야해.", --Remember you're looking for the server room.
["IDfa3dc6365e46d9e0"] = "서버실이야 - 찾아봐.", --Server room - find it.
["ID80fbc62c643a602e"] = "서버실을 찾아.", --Find the server room. 
["IDde5e3b49e0b29f5c"] = "좋아! 그게 서버야. 이제 연결해.", --Great! That's the server, now set up the connection.
["ID125fd94f4275c83e"] = "좋아, 이제 날 시스템에 로그인시켜줘.", --Great - now log me into the system.
["IDdd8469b350ff6ad8"] = "좋아. 이렇게 하면 연구실 문을 열수 있을꺼야.", --Good this should help us get the lab door open.
["ID7609a79ce10a9aa8"] = "접속했어, 연구실을 여는데 시간이 좀 걸릴거야.", --I'm in, might take a few to get the lab door open.
["IDe043a0d91e69a4b9"] = "좋아, 시스템에 침투했어. 곧 있으면 연구실 문이 열릴거야.", --OK, I'm in his system. Lab will open shortly.
["ID1d74eb81060b926e"] = "좋아, 접속했어. 최대한 빠르게 연구실을 열어볼게.", --OK, I'm in. I'll get the lab door open in no time.
["ID7f050461ca87b9ea"] = "경비가 우릴 못 보도록 해.", --Make sure the guards don't spot us now.
["IDad3c9206eeef0492"] = "경비의 시야에서 물러나.", --Stay clear of the guards.
["ID7d275fa22c14a1e7"] = "잘 하고 있어 - 경비에 들키지 않도록 해.", --We are doing good - keep away from the guards.
["ID9463b9f59dea5bf3"] = "전력을 다시 올려! 서버를 다시 복구해야해.", --Get the power to the server back on!
["ID60bc00a0dda280a7"] = "경찰이 전력을 내렸어, 다시 올려!", --They pulled the power, get it back on!
["ID878e2e0451ef121d"] = "연결이 끊겼어. 전력을 다시 올려야해.", --I lost connection, I need you to get the power back.
["ID6ef069cc394bd761"] = "젠장할! 서버가 전력이 끊겼어! 다시 전력을 올려!", --Damn it! I lost power to the server! Get it back up!
["IDa9aeb4d19d32adc2"] = "좋았어, 다시 연결해.", --Good, now set up the connection again.
["ID051dd0afdd8b9a15"] = "좋아, 다시 연결해줘.", --Alright, connect me again.
["IDc8872f537aaaf517"] = "날 다시 연결해줘.", --Hook me up again.
["IDc8fbc51ae49583fa"] = "잘 했어. 연결되었어.", --Great job, I'm connected.
["ID0fbcf048f327b5d6"] = "연결됐어. 전력 계속 유지해줘.", --Got connection. Keep working.
["ID25534e972e7870ab"] = "전력을 계속 유지해줘. 연결됐어.", --Keep it steady. I'm connected.
["ID3cc0b1afd98267cb"] = "작업 완료! 연구실 문을 열어!", --It's done! Open the labdoor!
["ID6c1e1c20c30815f9"] = "좋아, 연구실 문의 잠금이 해제됐어. 이제 열어.", --OK, the lab door is unlocked - open it.
["IDf25c7d3206eb6b89"] = "좋아. 연구실에 들어왔어. 제대로 작동하는 핵융합 엔진을 찾아. 연구원의 메모를 확인하고 어느 건지 알아내!", --Alright, we are in. Find the correct working fusion engine. Check his notes. Figure it out!
["ID596523045cac36f9"] = "좋아, 박사분들! 그 화려한 공대 지식을 활용해서 어떤게 맞는 핵융합 엔진인지 알아내. 시작해!", --OK, doctors - bring your MIT skills. Figure out which one is the correct fusion engine. Go!
["IDaee2fdaf369e8b77"] = "아. 그래... 보니까, 여기 엔진이 생각보다 많은데. 맞는 엔진을 찾아봐.", --Ah OK... So, seems to be a bit too many of them here. Fusion Engines that is. Find the correct one.
["ID1191b070ade8036c"] = "이봐... 맞는 엔진이 어떻게 생겼는지 보여주는 힌트같은 거 안 보여?", --Guys... Can you see any hints on what the correct one should look like?
["ID258931749828054f"] = "연구원의 서류, 메모나 컴퓨터를 확인해봐. 어떤 것이 맞다고 써둔 힌트는 여기 어딘가에 있을거야.", --Check his papers, notes and computers. Anything for a hint on what is correct here.
["ID95cee4ece0d9faf2"] = "이런 젠장할, 이거 너무 어려운 과학 지식들 뿐이군. 너희 머리 좀 굴려봐. 색깔이나 화학 성분같은게 단서가 될 수도 있을꺼야.", --Shit this is top science stuff - use those brains - any color code, chemicals or such can be a clue.
["ID1ea92bdbb6b6859e"] = "좋아, 헬기가 착륙할수 있도록 조명탄을 설치해.", --Great, Set off the flare so the chopper can land!
["IDb776252e6e5ace84"] = "헬리콥터가 여기로 오도록 하기 위해서 조명탄을 터트려.", --Pop the flare so we can bring the chopper in.
["ID8300b5c1705ce0ac"] = "위치를 표시해 - 조명탄을 사용하면 헬리콥터가 올꺼야.", --Mark the landing - use the flare and the chopper will come in.
["ID5e68426f0eec1c08"] = "좋아, 헬리콥터가 오고있어.", --Alright, the chopper is on its way.
["ID98406a5f6fbce01e"] = "헬리콥터가 오고있어. 기다려.", --Chopper is on its way. Stay put.
["ID1d989a18c5837998"] = "좋아, 헬리콥터가 엔진을 실으러 오고 있어.", --OK, chopper is coming in to pick up that Fusion Engine.
["ID589a40cd7e44fa0f"] = "좋아, 헬리콥터가 오고있어. 시제품을 준비해.", --OK, chopper's coming in, get the prototype ready.
["ID159f189104d75ef9"] = "좋아, 헬리콥터가 왔어. 엔진을 싣어.", --OK, chopper is here - get the engine loaded up.
["ID6f1387f69fda1075"] = "헬리콥터가 착륙하고 있어. 엔진을 싣고 이게 맞길 바라자고.", --Helicopters landing. Load up the engine and hope it is the one.
["IDc016ccb47a29d8d9"] = "엔진을 던져 넣어!", --Throw in the engine!
["IDe1075d7f6eb3d167"] = "엔진을 실어!", --Load it in!
["IDcbc4eb6cdc309460"] = "좋아! 우리가 엔진을 감정할 수 있도록 조종사가 엔진을 가지고 올거야.", --Alright! He'll bring it over here so we can inspect it.
["IDe541651b3132c7ec"] = "좋아, 조종사가 우리에게 되돌아온다. 감정해볼게.", --OK, he flies it to us. We will verify it.
["ID8563b9e5c0334da3"] = "엔진이 도착하면 내가 감정시켜볼게. 어디 가지말고 가만히 있어.", --Once here I will have it verified. Stay put. 
["ID9613a35e2c188633"] = "엔진 받았어. 내가 애들 시켜서 감정해볼게.", --We've got the engine, I'll have my guy here inspect it.
["ID85ebc1ebd2afc9b0"] = "조종사가 엔진을 가지고 왔어. 사람을 시켜서 감정해보지. 만약 이게 맞는거라면 탈출해도 좋아. 그러니깐 조금만 버텨줘.", --He delivered the engine. I'll have my man here inspect it, and if it's the right one we're good to go. So hang tight for a sec.
["IDb204af7793dddf12"] = "좋아. 우리가 감정하고 있어... 지금까지는 괜찮은데... 지금 시험을 하고 있어...", --OK, we're inspecting it... So far so good... He's running tests now...
["ID8cbafad0db49eb2b"] = "우리가 운이 나빴나 보군. 이거는 아니야. 다시 다른 엔진을 가져와줘. 다시 엔진을 공수할 헬리콥터를 보낼게.", --Looks like we're out of luck. This one's no good. Go get me another. I'm sending the chopper back to pick it up.
["IDd13c51245ee43b77"] = "미안해, 친구들. 감정사가 이건 아니라 하는군. 헬리콥터가 다른 엔진을 공수하러 가기위해 방금 출발했어. 이번엔 옳은 엔진을 찾길 바래.", --Sorry guys, he says this ain't the one. The chopper will be back in a few so you can get another one over here, hopefully the right one.
["ID4084e641639cc51d"] = "젠장할, 이거 오작동하는데! 다른 엔진을 가져오기 위해 헬리콥터를 다시 보낼게.", --Damn it, this one seems to be malfunctioning! I'm sending the chopper back to pick up another one.
["IDa2f611addfadcf51"] = "이거 죄다 망가지고 연기가 나는데. 연구실에서 새거 하나 갖고와 줘.", --All broken and smoking this one. Get me a fresh one from the lab.
["ID7b009951f4c8dc9f"] = "그래! 바로 이거야! 너희를 데려갈 헬리콥터를 보낼게. 조금만 버텨!", --Yes! This is the one. I'm sending the helicopter to pick you up! Hang tight!
["ID51c18542423f2221"] = "아주 좋아! 이거야. 핵융합 엔진의 파워를 제대로 보여주는군. 고마워 친구들, 이제 거기서 탈출해.", --Sweet! That's the one. Fusion power in full swing. Thanks guys. Now get out of there. 
["ID7c5041c1d1920203"] = "핵융합 반응이 확인됐어 - 모두 올바르고 바로 이거야. 거기서 빠져나와!", --Fusion reaction is confirmed - all good and green. You guys skip out of there !
["ID5e5cfbf7f87ad658"] = "잘했어, 친구들! 이거 맞는 것인거 같아. 빨리 빠져나오는게 좋을거야. 저번에 찾은 비행기 열쇠를 사용해.", --Nice work guys! This seems to be the right one! You guys better head out of there ASAP. Use the plane keys you found.
["ID2dbb206ef3da300c"] = "아하, 이거야! 상온 핵융합이 일어나는군. 너희들 아직도 발명가의 비행기 열쇠 가지고 있지, 기억나? 거기서 빠져나와!", --Aha! That's it! Cold Fusion, right here. You've got the keys to his airplane, remember? Get the hell out of there!
["ID1b5205a325542a38"] = "닥터 판타스틱이 다름없군! 너희 정말 똑똑한데. 너희가 고른 엔진은 맞는 엔진이야. 이제 돈을 많이 받겠지! 이제 거기서 탈출해! 헬리콥터가 그쪽으로 가고 있어.", --Dr Fantastic! You guys sure are smart. We got the right engine and you are rich. Now make it out of there! Chopper is incoming.
["IDb514a21e2b8591f9"] = "이보시오, 닥터 판타스틱 양반! 한 번에 바로 맞췄군. 너희들 과학좀 하나본데 - 잘 했어, 제군들. 이제 그 똑똑한 머리를 사용해서 빠져나와! 비행기를 사용해.", --Mr Dr Fantastic Sir! You nailed it. Thats some science - well done team. Get your big brains out of there! Use the plane.
["ID9d1c73924f921b99"] = "좋아, 제군들! 여기서 빠져나갈 시간이야!", --Alright gentlemen! It's time to get the hell out of there!
["ID86cfeb8d443fd99f"] = "좋아, 배달 완료! 이제 거기서 빠져나오게 해주지.", --OK, you delivered! Now let me get you out of there.
["ID161a9a783c21df36"] = "잘 했어. 헬리콥터에 타서 우리의 봉급날을 맞이하자고.", --Well done. Get into the chopper and lets go get our PAYDAY.
["ID5e08f23043470e28"] = "미안해, 친구들. 조종사가 기름을 다시 채워야 한다는군... 시간이 좀 걸릴거야. 잠시동안만 기다려. 알아들었지?", --I'm sorry guys, the pilot says he needs to refuel... And it's gonna take a while. Just hang in there for a while, OK?
["ID2ccb02f8694848d1"] = "흐으음... 사소한 문제가 생겼어. 헬리콥터가 계속 왔다갔다해서 기름이 바닥났어. 다시 채우고 올거야. 버티고 있어!", --Hmm we got a slight problem. Chopper is running out of fuel after all these back and forths. He will be back after refueling. Hold you ground!
["ID7f0b7cb2113f17ce"] = "아... 이봐, 친구들. 헬리콥터를 위해 기름을 조금 채워야 해. 완전 기름이 바닥이야. 아마 10분에서 15분 정도를 버텨야 할꺼야.", --Ah... OK guys, we got a small refuling need for the chopper. He is dry. You guys gotta stay put for about 10 - 15 minutes. 
["ID08e74c6802bd1e44"] = "좋아, 조종사가 헬리콥터를 주유하고 있어. 내가 서두르라고 말은 했지만, 나 참...", --OK, he's refueling now. I've told him to hurry but...
["ID317f981dbdd11e5b"] = "좋아, 그가 헬리콥터를 주유하고 있어. 조금만 기다려 친구들!", --OK, he is filling up that chopper now. Hold on guys!
["ID1d6ec75d43531e72"] = "조종사가 헬리콥터를 주유하고 있어 - 곧 돌아올거야. 내가 장담하지.", --The pilot is refueling the chopper - he will be back soon I promise.
["ID43a49045dbb6c157"] = "좋았어! 조종사가 연료를 다 채우고 다시 가고 있어!", --Yes! He's fueled up and heading back!
["IDd735d02a50288382"] = "헬기가 다시 가고있어 - 너무 오래 시간을 끌어서 미안하군.", --Chopper is heading back- sorry it took so long.
["ID13fbbcfe7ea7ef6c"] = "드디어, 조종사가 너희에게 되돌아가고 있어. 상황을 지연시켜서 미안해.", --Finally, the chopper pilot is heading back to get you guys. Sorry for the hold up.
["ID09e3529a64d9c5e7"] = "블랙호크가 지붕 위! 상황이 안좋아, 친구들!", --Blackhawk on the roof! This looks bad guys!
["ID23bce37d1898b15c"] = "블랙호크! 블랙호크가 내려온다! 준비해, 제군들!", --Blackhawk! Blackhawk coming down! Gun up team!
["ID1610fcb6fd99068c"] = "지붕! 지붕! 블랙호크가 지붕 위에 있어!", --Roof, Roof! Blackhawk on the roof!
["ID06929fcdebf49ca5"] = "젠장! 경보가 울렸어! 이제 모든 집안에서 우리가 온걸 알아버렸군!", --Damn it! The alarm! The whole house knows we are coming now!
["ID721bf86bcb78f8bc"] = "", --The Harvest & Trustee Bank just got a fresh shipment of cash for transport runs out of town to casinos. I propose we have a little monetary ''intervention'' of our own.
["IDbe04a9fc00192c36"] = "", --I mean they don't need it that bad... So let's hit that vault.
["ID50213b8b32f67e58"] = "", --I know a single large deposit of cash was just made to the Harvest & Trustee bank from a Swedish furniture warehouse close by. We're going to go in and take that place down.
["ID2966d975034723c2"] = "", --It's a pretty good layout for us. Vault's in the back. You in?
["ID4d70c1e580c0f814"] = "", --Today's our lucky day - cash delivery from the airport to this bank, all sorts of denominations... So I propose we do a little money exchange of our own. 
["ID56cc5457665e970f"] = "", --We hit that vault and hit it hard. Ready?
["ID03daaded3ea48a7d"] = "", --A little cash goes a long way. The local Harvest & Trustee branch bank needs to be lightened of its load.  Let's do this bank hit, get their vault open, and fill our pockets a little. 
["ID42bfa8e0209d5380"] = "", --Standard bank job, if there is such a thing. This one looks cash-rich.
["ID250c1d24046e526f"] = "", --We got a cash situation in this bank. They have missed their delivery to the HQ this week. Don't everyone sigh all at once...
["IDbfbbb73314098e2c"] = "", --PAYDAY is this week which means the currency's here now. Which means we are too.
["ID3e353bcb290d4541"] = "", --Cash job in the branch bank. Let's hit this thing. Should be a good win.
["ID0ff1019738ef888e"] = "", --Another day, another bank. We can liberate some cash, I'm sure.
["IDe0ffd289a53ece2a"] = "", --I'd feel bad about hitting another bank if they felt bad about hitting us. So I don't. Let's cash out.
["IDf4fab5da5e27d96a"] = "", --Shame about all these banks we're hitting, but we all have expenses. Wolf's lifestyle isn't cheap. Go time.
["IDbcf28805f63e9d5d"] = "", --This is a hit on a small bank but it doesn't mean it'll be easy. We're going for cash: you want to get into the bank vault, get the thermal drill out, crack the vault, bag up the cash and escape at our van.
["IDd8dc21ac0cde3c9b"] = "", --Oh - my guy stashed the thermal drill around the back of the bank. Good luck out there people.
["ID3ee42fffa4220b71"] = "", --Just because this is a bank job for cash doesn't mean it's gonna be easy. You need to get into the bank vault, try to control the civilians and tellers so they don't hit the alarm.
["IDe3bb3988aad7d868"] = "", --The manager might have a key too. I'd wish you luck, but you don't need it, right? 
["IDc6745c1ab1e56032"] = "", --We're robbing this bank for cash, pure and simple. You need to get into the bank vault using a thermal drill - there are tons of cameras and I heard a guy mention a security room at an establishment I frequent... But not sure.
["IDebf65a6f61af65e7"] = "", --Get the loot back to the escape car and we're home free. Good luck!
["ID03b6bf048446934c"] = "좋아, 필요한 써멀 드릴은 주차장 어딘가에 있을거야. 일을 개시하기 전에 가져가. 그걸로 금고를 뚫을 수 있을거야. 그리고 카메라와 은행 직원들을 조심해. 들어가기 전에 주변을 잘 살펴보고. 그리고 명심해, 돈이 최고야.", --OK, the thermal drill you need for the vault is somewhere in the parking lot. Get it before you do your takedown. Then you can go hit that vault. Watch for cameras and bank employees. Do your homework before you go in and remember cash is king.
["ID9111c7e1be4ae1ff"] = "좋아 얘들아, 내 부하가 은행 금고에 쓸 써멀 드릴을 주차장에 숨겨놨어, 그걸 먼저 챙겨. 경비들 조심하고, 보안 카메라 눈에 띄지 않도록 해 - 카메라가 있는 곳에는 보통 경비실도 있어... 돈 벌 시간이다.", --OK folks, my guy stashed the thermal drill for the bank vault in the parking lot, so get that first. Watch for guards, keep an eye out for cameras - where there's cameras there's usually a security room... Money time.
["ID76b5172a316cc0a9"] = "", --Got word that a certain local entrepreneur has been filling safe deposit boxes. I vote we look into it.
["ID4a8603b0763e9b2b"] = "", --Who doesn't love a secret, am I right? We've got a bank vault full of 'em to look into.
["IDd887d8146dfa8af3"] = "", --Happy birthday. Vault full of freshly loaded safe deposit boxes. Who's in?
["IDf736992c59a5282c"] = "", --Looks like we have an opportunity to crack some deposit boxes.
["ID3651b2475f72c5ca"] = "", --Got a deposit box opportunity in this bank. I have inside info.
["IDf8dca8b8d2c40b04"] = "", --You know I love safe deposit jobs. And this one sounds sweet...
["ID198d8f719805be75"] = "", --We might have a very valuable object in this bank. I have insurance papers backing that up.
["ID4307c3d861a1c7c3"] = "", --I got word one of the Harvest & Trustee banks just had a big run on safe deposit rentals from a teller I used to uh, speak to, socially. I think we should get into the vault and strip those boxes bare... You with me?
["ID720045c944cebbb9"] = "", --Looks like the local Trustee bank had someone renting a whole lot of safe deposit boxes. Now I don't know what's in them, and don't ask how I know, but I think this is a bank job we can't miss.
["IDf2194f80b7b935ce"] = "", --Let's get into that vault.
["ID2b905ae26b60be71"] = "", --Now we're getting into the bank vault. This job is about deposit boxes. You need to get in there and drill that vault. Case the bank first. They're wired out the ass with security cameras and trigger-happy guards.
["ID1af84b5d4d939c01"] = "", --Get the vault open with the thermal drill, then get the safe deposit boxes open - you might want a saw - and then carry your loot to the escape van.
["ID4404044797f29dc6"] = "", --OK, this is a bank job, but it's a safe deposit hit so it's a little different. You need to go in, careful to watch guards and cameras, drill the vault, crack it, then get whatever's in those safe deposit boxes.
["IDec5ebe7270fcc8a6"] = "", --Take as much as we need, but get more if you feel lucky. Then bag it, and get to the escape van. Let's do this!
["IDd6b80d8b9b36ea34"] = "좋아 친구들, 나는 이번건이 홈런이길 바라. 먼저, 주차장에서 써멀 드릴을 가지고 와서 그 다음에 금고로 치고 들어가는 거야. 경비와 카메라를 조심해.", --OK guys I want this to be a homerun. First get the thermal drill from the parking lot. Then head in to hit the vault. Watch for guards and cameras. 
["IDf372cc859b94d516"] = "시민들이 눈치 챌수도 있을거야. 그렇게 내버려 두지마. 안전한 곳에서 보자.", --The civilians might get ideas. Don't let 'em have 'em. See you at the safe house.
["ID1dafe8e9bc3a28f5"] = "좋아 얘들아, 내 사람이 신중하게 은행 금고를 열 써멀 드릴을 주차장에 숨겨놨어. 가져와서 은행금고를 열어.", --OK people, my contact thoughtfully stashed the thermal drill you're going to need to crack the bank vault somewhere in the parking lot. Get it, then hit the bank vault.
["ID59d7947f6387f762"] = "참고로 나라면 조심할꺼야. 이 은행근처는 사람이 많이 다닌다고. 개인금고들을 다 열어서 한번 신나는 하루를 지내보자고.", --I advise caution - this bank has a lot of traffic. Empty all those safe deposit boxes and make us all happy.
["ID823976147358304b"] = "", --Branch bank job with a twist, and the twist is golden. Bars, that is. Let's do our thing.
["IDcd9301c83edcc362"] = "", --OK this is your standard job only it's gold-plated, if you take my meaning. 
["ID74853639c393f23a"] = "", --OK, standard bank hit, only we're going for the gold drop off day. Gotta remain liquid, right?
["ID35e6901ea9c08b6d"] = "", --Crew this is hot off the wire. I have a gold deposit waiting for us. 
["IDf1bfa1713672cf01"] = "", --People I think this job is a gold mine. Almost literally. 
["IDe434dfe8e18aabf4"] = "", --I got an inside man who tells me the color of the money on this job is golden.
["IDb195085378cb6ff7"] = "", --Gold, gold, gold. Let's go dig in the vault, shall we?
["IDb742e0bcf485f70e"] = "", --You can't go wrong with gold. The Harvest & Trustee bank is trying to up its liquidity with a large deposit. It's something we should take advantage of, don't you think?
["ID24894b69827ad736"] = "", --Let's get into that vault and get our gold out.
["ID752608cb5547ab3e"] = "", --The Harvest & Trustee bank just got a big gold shipment from South Africa. I think we should make it go away. I can't see they'll miss them much.
["ID6aeacc97ed371617"] = "", --Gear up and let's go drill that vault. I want us to feel like rich dwarves. 
["IDfe9502e8412773f4"] = "", -- In unstable times like these, gold's all you can really depend on.  So who wants to go stabilize our economic future? The Harvest & Trustee bank vault awaits.
["IDaf055ec20d4e8c85"] = "", --You up for it? Because I've got a contact who says they're just gotten a south African gold shipment that would be a shame to make go missing...
["IDbd0b3b4529307937"] = "", --Like I said, this is a bank job for gold. It's a small bank, but they've got a lot of security and a lot of customers. You're going to have to work hard to keep this from turning ugly. Drill the vault, the floor plans say it's around back.
["IDcaa113ec791c68fd"] = "", --Bag up the loot - gold is heavy remember - and wait for me to send the escape car. Clear? Oh - my guy left the thermal drill to get into the vault out back. Let's roll.
["IDda75322b1fd54300"] = "", --Gold is golden. You're going to work hard on this one. Get into the bank, control the room, open that bank vault with the thermal drill... I'll try to have my guy drop it off for you.
["ID7a3f1e975175c7b9"] = "", --Then get the gold out. It's heavy, so bring strong people. Get the loot to the escape van - at least as much as you think you can. Good luck!
["IDf2e6c7d7e66ccf1f"] = "", --We're going in for a golden bank robbery. It'd be smart to look around before you make your move, lots of security, then get in and drill the vault. Lift the gold into bags - remember it's heavy.
["ID7c0d1f68026a41cc"] = "", --Then back to the escape van and bang, we're rich! Go with grace.
["ID3aa44c947ebb7ee0"] = "은행을 정찰해. 내 부하가 써멀 드릴을 그 지역 주변에 놔두고 왔을꺼야, 아마도 은행 뒷 편일꺼야, 찾아봐. 그리고 가져가서 네가 할 일을 해. 금덩이가 기다리고 있어.", --Recon the bank. My guy dropped a thermal drill somewhere on the premises, around the back of the bank, find it. Then get in there and do your thing to the vault. Gold awaits.
["ID23fa845779e6778f"] = "좋아 친구들. 내부에 있는 내 부하가 너희들이 금고에 사용할 써멀 드릴을 은행 주변에 숨겨놨어. 주변을 정찰해서 찾아봐. 준비되면 금고로 가. 이번 작업은, 정말 금빛일거야.", --OK folks, my inside man stashed the thermal drill you're gonna need for the vault around the back. recon the spot to find it. Make your move on the vault when you're ready. This job, It's gonna be golden.
["IDd9f670b0d5fac29e"] = "좋아. 이 일을 위해 써멀 드릴이 필요할거야. 내 부하들이 은행 뒤에 숨겨놨어. 가져가서 금고 일에 착수해. 보안 카메라와 시민들을 조심하라구. 가서 금을 가져와, 친구들.", --OK, You're gonna need a thermal drill for this gig. My guy stashed it around the back of the bank. Get it and get to work on the vault.  Keep in mind there's security cameras and lots of civilians. Go win the gold, folks.
["ID63899831e80bfca2"] = "", --OK team ready your gear. This is what we do best, bank jobs. Get your loot bags checked, leave your cell phones home, bring the gloves, load up those guns and get the PAYDAY attitude on.
["ID72bd29989de9c3c5"] = "", --There's a bank vault we need to hit... 
["IDbb329bad775501f7"] = "", --OK crew. You know how it goes, it's a bank hit. Ditch your phones, get your mind condition one and snap on the gloves. We're going to hit this branch bank. They're all over this town.
["IDa046906e22d65a2b"] = "", --Harvest & Trustee. My contacts says it's juicy as hell. In and out. You with me? 
["ID711c5708026e0d59"] = "", --People, you've probably done this a dozen times. Hitting the Harvest & Trustee Bank over on 5th.  No idea what's in there but we know it's gonna be sweet. Get that vault open and away we go. You in?
["ID03d5f0eb39b1b336"] = "", --OK people, my guy says this is a good time to hit the bank. Turns out the Harvest & Trustee bank manager should have kept his mouth shut. Anything could be in here.
["ID15af01ec6adc44c1"] = "", --Government secrets, dirty laundry, the Hope Diamond... You never know. Let's hit this bank and find out, shall we?
["ID83787707c1e71967"] = "", --The Harvest & Trustee is a medium-size branch bank, vault in the back, a few different entries. Case the place first... You're going to want to get into the vault, drill it, get whatever's inside out of there and back to the escape car.
["ID0035ca55cb7b6952"] = "", --My man is going to leave the thermal drill you need for the job out back. Good luck.
["IDaeef81b3b143c05f"] = "", --The Harvest & Trustee is a vulnerable bank so I see an opportunity for us. Case it so you can find out where. You're going to need to get into the vault using a thermal drill, get whatever's in there bagged up and moved back to the escape car. Use your judgment and don't be greedy... Good luck, folks.
["ID892734bd6474d468"] = "", --You're going to need to get into the vault using a thermal drill, get whatever's in there bagged up and moved back to the escape car. Use your judgment and don't be greedy... Good luck, folks.
["ID4aedaa0205156e7e"] = "", --These Harvest & Trustee branch banks are easy pickings for guys like you. Case the bank so you can find out its weakness.
["IDb253e3ff7ff5a20a"] = "", --Watch the cameras, usually these branches have security rooms where you can kill the cameras. You're going to need to get into the vault, bag up the loot, and move it back to the escape car. 
["IDb5f70f0c30cf5fec"] = "", --Use your judgment and don't be greedy. My guy left the thermal drill for the bank vault out back. Good luck, folks.
["IDb316fd69c2d64615"] = "", --This Harvest & Trustee branch bank has its weaknesses. Case it so you can find out where. You're going to need to get into the vault using a thermal drill, get whatever's in there bagged up and moved back to the escape car. Use your judgment and don't be greedy. Remember bank cameras usually have security rooms, but I guess you know that. Good luck, folks!
["IDf8ae3e8eb1985451"] = "좋아, 이번엔 은행이야. 조언해주자면 그 곳을 먼저 조사하고 그 다음 뒤쪽 주차장 어딘가에 있는 써멀 드릴을 집어 들어. 그 다음 금고를 네가 원하는대로 처리하도록 해. 은행에는 경비실이 있으니까 조심하고.", --OK, this is the bank. I advise casing the place, then grab the thermal drill from the back parking lot somewhere. Hit the vault however you want. There's usually a security room so be cautious. 
["IDbd397ec22e2cde9b"] = "도둑질 할 시간이다. 주차장에 숨겨져있는 써멀드릴을 가져와. 그 다음은 너에게 달렸어. 여기서 우리가 뭘 훔칠지 모르지만, 기억해, 시민들을 잘 관리하고. 사람들이 경보나 핸드폰을 이용하지 못하게 해. 은신처에서 보자.", --Robbery time. Get the thermal drill stashed in the parking lot. Then it's up to you. I don't know what we're gonna get here but remember: keep the civilians in check, don't let 'em use alarms or phones. See you at the safe house.
["IDaaf447d41262f585"] = "다들 어떻게 하는지 알거야. 내 부하가 주차장에 써멀 드릴을 놔두고 왔어. 안으로 들어가기 전에 가져가. 감시를 좀 하면 더 좋을거야.", --Everyone, you know how it's done. My guy dropped the thermal drill in the parking lot, so grab that before you make your move inside. Some surveillance would be smart.
["ID5ec1ac633a481e04"] = "준비가 되면 드릴을 가동시켜. 안에 뭐가 있는지는 모르겠지만, 이번 기회를 놓칠수는 없지.", --Drill the vault when you are ready. I don't know what's here but I like our chances.
["ID0f996495ba962c8a"] = "", --It's bank job time people. Mask up and let's see what we got.
["ID73b4ed4dcf2f5f41"] = "", --Who's ready to do a bank job? I know I am.
["ID261e43827634459c"] = "", --Guys this bank just seems right. Don't know the load but it should be big.
["IDa1d7520ca23bbadb"] = "", --Pretty sweet line on a bank - after a while they all start to look the same I bet. Let's do it.
["IDbb479f3d907160bd"] = "", --This branch bank is ready for the taking. Let's do this.
["IDe9bb1ccfc71c1e9e"] = "", --Time for a bank job guys. I got a perfect one for you.
["ID773a7d5b74ac5e44"] = "은행을 정찰해. 내 부하가 써멀 드릴을 어딘가에 놔두고 왔는데... 은행 뒷 편이야, 찾아봐.", --Recon the bank. My guy dropped a thermal lance somewhere on the premises... Around the back of the bank, find it.
["ID306f0b034afd6afd"] = "좋아 친구들. 내부에 있는 내 부하가 너희들이 금고에 사용할 써멀 드릴을 은행 주변에 숨겨놨어. 주변을 정찰해서 찾아봐.", --OK folks, my inside man stashed the thermal lance you're gonna need for the vault around the back. Recon the spot to find it.
["ID1421176b4ff1c004"] = "좋아... 이 일을 위해 써멀 드릴이 필요할거야... 내 부하들이 은행 뒤에 숨겨놨어. 가져가서 일에 착수해.", --OK... You're gonna need a thermal drill for this gig... My guy stashed it around the back of the bank. Get it and get to work.
["ID328d7e5fbfa523d4"] = "좋아, 금고안에 금이 있어.", --OK, the vault's got the gold. 
["IDcd7187f656a106c4"] = "알겠지, 우린 개인 금고 때문에 온거야.", --Alright, we're in for deposit boxes.
["IDe56a95ce0698f53f"] = "이건 곧장 현금을 터는 방식이야. 어떻게 하는지 알지?", --It's a straight cash hit. You know how this goes.
["ID08eb57cd7868fdd2"] = "난 은행을 사랑하지. 돈 냄새가 가득하거든.", --I love banks. The smell of all that money.
["IDc4e5e6b1dceda55d"] = "누구 은행 일 좀 보고 싶은사람?", --Who wants to do a little banking?
["ID96eb644d30398f6f"] = "다들 현금 인출할 준비해.", --Everyone get ready to make a little withdrawal now.
["ID71ff7ce06314311d"] = "열렸다! 돈 챙겨!", --It's open! Bag the money!
["ID668f609dfd381e0c"] = "개인 금고를 한번 보는게 좋을껄. 뭔가 값어치있는게 있을거야.", --You might wanna look through some of the deposit boxes, could be something valuable.
["ID34ab40f905b55b7e"] = "좋았어, 차로 가져오도록, 모퉁이 돌면 있어.", --Alright, bring it to the van, it's right around the corner.
