["ID4a8fdb302fd5a22b"] = "좋은 생각이야, 판자로 녀석들을 조금이나마 막을수 있을꺼야.", --Good thinking, boards will slow them down.
["ID7aa6eaae8a9a86d8"] = "", --They had no chance at all. I don't think the National Guard could have stopped you.
["ID6c99873bc28cee43"] = "", --Loot's ours. One thing I like about bank jobs is the instant gratification. Good work.
["IDca8f4d6586fb7187"] = "", --Safe house vault is going to be a little crowded tonight. Nicely done, folks.
["IDff5756736388134b"] = "", --Time to get out of dodge - let's split the loot at the safe house and take the weekend off.
