["ID5c85012c2a199090"] = "사고 하나 크게 났구만. 경찰들이 너희 쉴 시간을 내주지는 않을테니, 빨리 일어서!", --That was one hell of a crash. The cops aren't gonna give you a break though, so get on your feet!
