["ID849b9c5a821e5f6c"] = "좋아! 날 당장 연결해 줘!", --Great! Now hook me up!
["ID0a908410b02f0176"] = "아, 좋아! 좀 흥미진진한 것들이 나오고 있어!", --Ah, OK! I'm getting some juicy stuff here!
["ID451e59ba07017472"] = "보아하니 무기와 금을 바꾸는 거래였던것 같아. 그것도 이 워싱턴 DC에서 이루어졌어.", --Seems like the deal was a gold arms transaction. Made here in DC.
["IDfc9661260d1fe966"] = "왜 코끼리가 이 일을 해달라고 했는지 이제 알겠어. 상원의원이 상당한 양의 금괴를 거래했구만!", --I get why the Elephant wants this. It is tons of gold in this deal!
["ID7149ffb8a964b8e3"] = "이런, 들키지 말았어야 했어. 이 거래로 받은 노다지를 뺏을 수 있었을텐데.", --Ah, we should have sneaked this. Tons of gold in this deal.
["IDd6de96bcc45ddbca"] = "좋아, 상원의원이 거래하는 영상을 찾았어... 미친. 콧대가 하늘을 찌르는군.", --Alright, I found video of him doing the deal... It is insane. He sure is a show-off.
["IDf1f81fa16a956813"] = "이런! 우리네 착하신 상원의원님께서 거래 중에 파티까지 하셨나보군 - 보아하니 무기-금에다가 코카인까지 거래한거 같아.", --Oh, my! Seems like the good senator did the deal and partied at the same time - looks like a arms-gold-coke deal.
["IDd92ce2e0f0ca67d4"] = "좋았어! 스캔들급 물건이 여기 있군. 우리 의원님이 정부의 무기들을 무장단체에 팔아넘겼어 - 그것도 금을 받고 말이야. 상원의원측이 이걸 좋아하지는 않겠지.", --OK! We got some real scandal stuff here. He sold government arms to a rogue state - got paid in gold. The Democrats aint gonna like this.
["IDd9b5a024d520d33a"] = "언론이 이 불쌍한 녀석을 물고뜯는 파티를 벌이게 되겠군. 심지어 거래를 공공사무소에서 벌인거 같아!", --Press are going to party on this poor guy. Seems the deal went down in public office too!
["IDfad02613441c01f4"] = "내가 이걸 파일로 만들어서 언론에 바로 생방송으로 보낼 준비를 할께.", --I'll pack this into files and get ready to stream it up to the press.
["ID4b0081ed48d1b6e7"] = "그 뉴스 피드를 계속 살려놔야지 내가 너희들을 거기서 빠져 나오게 할 방법을 찾을수 있어.", --Keep that news feed alive and I'll start getting you a way out of there.
["IDbc745f565ca29f41"] = "이정도면 누명을 씌우기엔 충분할거야 - 완벽하지는 않았지만, 그래도 보수는 받을수 있을꺼야. 여기서 나가게 해줄께!", --This will work as a frame - won't be fantastic, but we will get paid. Let's get you out!
["ID717b7c89f5cacfbf"] = "기가 막힌 아파트군! 하긴 무기 거래로 의원 급여에 짭짤하게 보탰을테니 말이야.", --What a flat! These arms deals sure are a nice addition to his senator pay.
["ID239ded5c875d6555"] = "이야... 여기 대단하군... 그 금괴를 찾아서 우리도 이런 곳을 장만하자.", --Man... This place... Find that gold and we can buy one of our own.
["IDb66ebddd54eace6d"] = "좋아, 조심해! 끝까지 조용히 잠입할만한 충분한 가치가 있는 곳이라고, 친구들. 경보를 울리지 않기만 하면 이 누명 씌우는 일은 완벽한 작업이 될거야!", --OK, be careful! It will be worth sneaking all the way through, boys. No alarms and this framing will be perfect!
["ID6be162493353d93b"] = "이 죽여주는 것들좀 봐. 이거 마련하려면 정부에서 일할때 공익사업을 엄청 했나본데.", --Look at all these nice things. Must have done a lot of public service in his career.
["ID84a409be2aa4c25a"] = "저게 공공사무실이라고? 와, 우리 직종을 잘못 선택한거 같은데.", --Public office. Wow, we are in the wrong line of work gentlemen.
["IDcc3b6d155c34c4c1"] = "저 경치 좀 봐...", --Look at the that view...
["ID6a498fd348c22728"] = "그래, 저기가 바로 백악관이야. 저곳에서는 무슨 귀중품이 있을까 궁금하군. 뭐, 일단 하던 일을 계속하자.", --Yes, that is the epicenter - right there. I wonder what kind of treasure that house can hold. OK, on with our heist here.
["ID8773571cbbf880c7"] = "백악관이라, 다음엔 저기를 한번 털어 볼수도 있겠는데.", --1600 Penn, maybe we go there for our next big score.
["IDa8fb1b4fd20a5aca"] = "아, 저기가 바로 금고야. 이 금고문을 이번에는 열 수 없어. 하지만 금괴가... 금괴들이 바로 안에 있는데! 칫, 두고 갈 수 밖에 없겠어.", --Ah, that is the vault guys. That door, we can't get through it this time. But the gold... The gold on the other side! Well, we got to leave it.
["ID1fab6b4cc44f3027"] = "금을 그냥 두고 가는 건 아쉽지만, 그래도 돈은 받을 수 있을 거야. 어쩌면 다시 오게 될지도 몰라.", --It feels bad to leave the gold, but we will get paid. Maybe we can return.
["IDc11c28ba38641ecc"] = "", --A little bird told me the Mendozas are flying in more weapons in preparation for the war with Hector. We go to their airport, find the weapons and take them all or destroy them.
["ID77888b3664ecb5ab"] = "", --Preferably take them as the money will be great that way.
["IDc2a7ad9fe5a4644b"] = "", --Hector wants to send a message in, quote en quote, blood and fire to the Mendoza cartel as they roll into their private airport. Might be tricky... But I think we can.
["IDfdf69008302d9f4b"] = "", --A little bird told me the Mendozas are flying in more weapons in preparation for the war with Hector.
["ID8b2acb6e4997e2fb"] = "", --We go to their little private airport, find the weapons and take them all or destroy them... But it's more profitable if we take them.
["ID53ab2bea82f61e9b"] = "", --And now Mendoza and his goons are down a lot of firepower. Hector's people will face a lot less resistance thanks to you. He might even appreciate us. Well done. 
["ID1ab08183ed52197e"] = "", --OK we're good to go. I'll get you guys cleared to the safe house. Their arsenal is gone. Their soldiers toothless.
["ID2dc0136ebbaf5cd5"] = "", --We pulled Mendoza's teeth on that job - destroying those weapons is gonna leave him with a lot more bark than bite. I bet Hector bumps us up the food chain for sure.
["IDa4439dca4ac9ba6a"] = "", --Well executed. Guns destroyed and Hector is informed. Let's cash in.
["ID39409df162cadcbb"] = "", --That was close. Good work disposing of those guns. Hector will move in his army now and we will have a very fine PAYDAY indeed.
["ID2cc630e4763a53bd"] = "", --You dont let me down. Hector will be proud of this work. We are in business for real.
["ID365bd43235386f52"] = "", --Good work people. This could have gone poorly but you managed to keep us in the black. Arms trading, anyone?
["IDf4566f383153e274"] = "", --Look like you are heavily loaded - that was all the guns right? I'll have to make it harder next time. Maybe wear a blindfold or something. Well done.
["ID978aab90b82ab9bc"] = "", --That worked like a charm. Well fought and well carried out if you know what I mean. PAYDAY is coming our way, well deserved.
["ID894672377fa24977"] = "", --More guns, more money. Great work. Hector is waiting for us.
["IDe873d1a927c0b9c5"] = "좋아, 공항은 바로 이 언덕 아래야. 철조망을 자르고 들어가서 무기를 실은 트럭이 있는 격납고를 찾아. 멘도자 갱들이 아마 거기 있을거야. 무기를 챙겨오거나 걔네들이 못쓰게 만들어버려.", --OK, the airport is just down the hill. Cut through the fence and find the hangar where the truck holding the cases is. The Mendozas will probably be there. Go get those weapons or make sure they don't. 
["ID95be916876a6c6cf"] = "너희들은 철조망을 통해 진입할꺼야. 무기들을 찾아서 여기로 가지고 와. 저 녀석들은 싸우지 않고서는 굴복하지 않을꺼야. 만약 상황이 힘들게 돌아간다면 - 무기들을 파괴해버려.", --You're gonna go in through the fence, find the guns and bring 'em back here. They're not going down without a fight. If it hits the fan out there - destroy the guns.
["IDc2e9cc942cc5c0dd"] = "맨도자 갱들이 창고에서 무기를 싣느라고 바쁠거야. 가서 그들이 전부 너랑 전쟁을 치르기 전에 빠르게 공격해. 그 녀석들의 무기를 챙기거나 파괴해버려.", --The Mendozas are going to be busy loading their guns in the warehouse. Go in and hit 'em fast before they go all Lord of War on you. Get those weapons or destroy 'em. 
["ID8176fc44d916b73c"] = "일단 진입하게 되면, 무기 케이스들을 찾아서, 무기들을 파괴하거나 가지고 돌아와. 만약 더 가져오고 싶으면, 너희가 원하는대로 해.", --Once you're in, find the crates and destroy them or bring them back. You want to do more, be my guest.
["IDfe9418ac850ce4c5"] = "", --OK, find a way inside, stay low, and keep an eye out for guards and cameras.
["IDa94dbc550f6e52dc"] = "", --Good, you are inside, now, locate the server room.
["ID69efab75f35dcfdc"] = "", --We're looking for a Gensec security door - the security room is in there.
["ID9678d052ee195538"] = "", --Should be a higher security type of door, look for a Gensec logo.
["IDe4f5779dc7012104"] = "", --Alright, locate the server room, and get inside, there's no point in disabling the alarms now.
["ID644727526f9f7907"] = "", --Alright, that's the door to the server room.
["ID48b54ef0c45e0eac"] = "", --It's alarmed, so don't open it yet. we need to disable the alarm first.
["ID25675e45d9bb840b"] = "", --Get that door open.
["IDbe74b65aa3540887"] = "", --Next up, the computer.
["ID301d606dd441a5e1"] = "", --Use that terminal - I want access to their systems.
["ID1e3027837355a5c3"] = "", --Alright, I'm in, hold on...
["ID46caca3c8ee53b82"] = "", --OK, I have access...
["IDfdb5faaec50eab89"] = "", --...There's 3 Gensec security boxes we need to disable.
["ID037f14c37e57aaf8"] = "", --...There's 2 Gensec security boxes we need to disable.
["ID88e08f353f041c5a"] = "", --...There's 1 Gensec security box we need to disable.
["IDe849e895812acc7f"] = "", --I've marked them for you - get to them, and cut the wire.
["ID1bb21152ef3068cc"] = "좋아.", --Good.
["ID14dc2d0ce7a296b6"] = "", --2 remaining.
["IDd20d545a3939671e"] = "", --1 remaining.
["ID9e482b635bbf4f05"] = "", --Get the last one.
["IDae87d434e9c8541b"] = "", --Great, that's it. Now you can open the door.
["ID972dd6ef44b2ec1c"] = "", --Ah, I see you already took care of the security boxes. Planning ahead, I like this.
["ID86a60b5b0252ae63"] = "", --What are you doing? Wait for me to mark them out. We need to cut the right wire.
["ID4613c87b6da7bde6"] = "들어갔어? 잘했어.", --You're inside? Good job.
["ID9131faba1ba132ee"] = "", --Now there's only one more door between you and the server.
["IDd023e3d59900a12d"] = "", --Open up that last door and get to the server.
["IDdaeea94b8879e5a7"] = "", --Awesome job gang! Last step - you need to dismantle the server and bring it to the car.
["ID23fff95052c2de7e"] = "", --Alright, you got it. Let's get out of here!
["ID8745071cbe02360a"] = "", --Don't mess up or get seen now. Almost there...
["ID849871e241424e8c"] = "", --There's a car waiting for you, just across the road.
["ID3ab55a03ab2e3d0b"] = "", --They didn't even see us coming. Great work! See you at the safe house.
["ID99913c6afcce92be"] = "", --Oh no, that's the alarm! Lets go to plan B.
["IDbeac88fd6e0ed492"] = "", --Get that server anyway you can!
["ID81284da028a7a70b"] = "", --What are you doing!? You didnt even make it inside, Let's go to plan B, and next time, stay low.
["IDa37d7b3f675bdcb8"] = "", --There are SWATs rappelling in to the office!
["ID78dac64e66d9955a"] = "", --Snipers across the alley!
["ID3c0bdc3792042604"] = "", --Snipers! On the roof.
["ID65b738c4ff23bbe7"] = "", --Now Hector tells me we need to hit the Mendozas themselves for information. Where they keep their money, in fact.
["ID4326b8ae204a4888"] = "", --Lucky for us, someone in the Mendoza cartel gave up info that they're being investigated by the FBI. So all we need to do is hit the local FBI office handling the cartel to get the data.
["ID824ed09cf5c51b29"] = "", --And yes I know. Out of the frying pan, into the fire...
["ID38070b4604db1366"] = "", --Wow. This would make a great tv movie. For someone who isn't you. Anyway now we know where the Mendoza bank is located. 
["ID8c839f83b090046b"] = "", --Terrific. Because of you we know where all the Mendoza cash is stashed. It's one of the Trustee branch banks. I guess you know what comes next, huh?
["ID139a63a1579d829b"] = "", --Good work, crew. Now if Hector knew we just hit the FBI for the info he might worry a bit. But what Hector doesn't know won't hurt him. Let's go banking, shall we?
["ID5ec1af7e37c73e4c"] = "", --Well I guess the whole keep a low profile is now out of the question. On the other hand, even bad publicity is good publicity, and we got what we came for. Well done. 
["IDba422e5e6b8a5ff4"] = "", --It's pretty hot out there. In fact I would bet you are more wanted than Mendoza now. Hector will probably think we're behind it, not being stupid. 
["ID55633c41bb834f3d"] = "", --Let's just fix this bank and burn the Mendoza money ASAP. We can find you new identities after.
["ID02b192ebb28058de"] = "FBI 임시 사무실이 길건너 있어. 잠입해 들어가서 내가 서버에 접속 할 수 있게 해주면 멘도자 갱들에 관한 또다른 정보들이 있는지 볼게.", --The FBI temp office is across the street. Sneak inside, get me access to their server room and see what other Mendoza info is lying around.
["ID4fd3d383729660fe"] = "네가 발각되면 무슨 일이 일어날지 굳이 말 할 필요는 없겠지.", --I don't think I need to mention what happens if you get found out.
["ID808fe2d6d5c23e3c"] = "우린 지금 벌집에 들어가는거야. 그러니까 벌집을 차지 말자고?", --You're going into the hornet's nest. So don't kick the damn thing, huh. 
["ID791d7522e73af253"] = "숨어 들어서 야근하는 수사관을 지켜봐. 멘도자에 관한 정보가든 FBI 서버를 찾아서 나와.", --Sneak in, check the cameras to see the Feds working those thankless hours. Get the Mendoza info on the FBI server and get out. Go easy.
["ID8e34b2a239274814"] = "좋아 친구들, 바로 본진으로 가는거야. 그 곳안에는 우리가 필요한 정보가 있을꺼야. 그리고 더 많은 경비들도 있겠지. 서버룸을 찾아서 돈을 보관하고 있는 은행에 관한 정보를 빼내와. 나머지는 내가 알아서 조사할께.", --OK folks. Going straight to the source. Inside that place is the info we need - and way more law than we want to be close to. Find their server room and get the info on the bank. I'll do the rest.
["IDe583d88eb120291c"] = "", --OK guys, get into the bank and find the vault and drill it open. Make sure no one triggers the alarm or escapes.
["ID733f30d99e9eb4a5"] = "", --Holy shit! Looks like they've electrified the vault!
["ID761fcf4280d8925b"] = "", --Get to the generator on the roof and shut it down.
["IDff194fdef639bca5"] = "", --That should do it, you can place the drill now.
["ID69054af6506d68d5"] = "", --Excellent! Keep that drill going.
["ID30d831b2936d5239"] = "", --OK, Hector wants us to record this so first set up the camera.
["ID72e21d135f8e1dbb"] = "", --Now, torch the money...
["ID1aec2bbe9344bcbc"] = "", --OK, while we wait for the money to burn you can open up some of those deposit boxes, what ever we find in there is ours.
["IDd394c665f728e09c"] = "", --OK, that's enough, get the recording and lets get out of here.
["IDb6db4b7707ed70e8"] = "", --The car will pick you up around the corner.
["ID10de93ad8e412d25"] = "", --A civilian escaped, must have called the cops!
["ID3974119936a5c03b"] = "", --Someone pressed the alarm button.
["IDfb119f4d1f6d8b9a"] = "", --The surveillance guard triggered the alarm.
["IDf4893b0a191bb123"] = "", --Expect cops any second now.
["ID7d915a9b0dd7b3fd"] = "", --Someone called the police!
["ID73b4bb1855560919"] = "", --There's a SWAT helicopter on the roof.
["ID3b65273a68270674"] = "", --There are snipers on the surrounding buildings.
["ID14b596106abec645"] = "", --This is the place, people... This bank here holds all the Mendoza capital north of the border.
["IDaf9579fc79a46df1"] = "", --Little old grandmothers walk right by their blood money every day. Hidden in plain sight, Hector says. At least $100 million in black cash.
["ID7e8481ff592be545"] = "", --What you're gonna do is go in, control the crowd, get into the vault without the alarms going off. Then set a fire, and film yourself doing it. Hector wants it that way.
["ID4f5e545424aabdf0"] = "", --Hector got the footage. I'm told he laughed long and hard. And now the FBI looks impossibly incompetent, which takes a lot of heat off of us. Great work.
["ID4092991069ea7ad6"] = "", --I know that was a lot of money to send up in smoke and I apologize, I know it goes against your nature, but hopefully you find the compensation competitive.
["IDfa6d08cd161b0add"] = "", --And it was the right thing not to mess with Hector here - playing with fire would have gotten us burned.
["IDedd9ad6c899d8ec3"] = "", --FBI in disarray. A lot of people about to get called into their bosses' office. Mendoza crippled and we're about to get paid. Nice burn, folks.
["IDbd0359acd0619ab4"] = "", --Mendoza's not going to like that outcome. But we should. Well done. Go get paid.
["IDb2561ecb2ee28953"] = "", --The Mendoza cartel just got knocked on its ass. Nothing hurts like taking a financial beating and they just took a big one. Hector will rise and that's good fortune for us down the line. 
["IDbea28bdfcdca3421"] = "", --Burning 100 million dollars is a hell of a thing. It makes me feel like a real banker. All in a day's work. See you at the safe house. 
["ID291e543471c2e74a"] = "저번처럼만 하면 돼: 몰래 들어가. 카메라와 경비, 그리고 경보를 주의하도록 해. 빠르게 진입하도록해. 하지만 너무 서두르지는 말라고.", --One more time: sneak in, watch for cameras, guards and any other alarms. Go in fast but careful. Don't get sloppy.  
["ID013bda042ea89bc3"] = "그리고 난뒤에 돈을 찾아서, 불태우도록 해. 그리고 내가 준 카메라로 녹화하는걸 절대 잊지 말고.", --Then find that money, torch it, and for god's sake record it with the camera I gave you.
["IDaaeb299d276f0688"] = "헥터가 우리가 돈을 몰래 빼돌리지 않았다는 증거가 필요하다고 하더라고.", --Hector wants proof we didn't just swipe the cash.
["IDefbe43f5b9e816e1"] = "좋아 모두들. 은행으로 가서 써멀 드릴로 금고를 뚫은 다음에 돈을 불태워. 녹화하는 거 잊지 마.", --OK folks: you go in, breach the vault with the thermal lance, burn the money and remember to film it. 
["ID7ab339f2a356ca55"] = "헥터는 세계에 보여줄, 그리고 우리가 한 일을 보여줄 영상이 필요하다구.", --Hector needs footage to show the world and, well, for our own safety.
["ID932c1c4280ba54b3"] = "적어도 나는 카르텔을 건드리고 싶지는 않거든.", --I'd rather not piss off the cartel.
["IDfcab1f942904b101"] = "Trustee 은행이 바로 앞에 있어. 들어가서, 금고를 열고, 돈을 태우고, 모든걸 영상으로 찍어서 나오도록해. FBI가 지금 눈에 불을 켜고 너희들을 찾아다니고 있으니까, 빠르고 깔끔하게 일을 처리하도록해. 자, 시작하자.", --Trustee bank is up ahead. Go in, find the vault, blaze the money, video the whole thing and get out. FBI is on the highest alert so make it quick and clean. Let's do it.
["ID95c53a0b74c30452"] = "상점 안에 들어가서, 시민들을 통제하고, 감시 카메라로 처리해, 그리고 일을 끝내버려.", --Get into the store, watch the civilians, watch the cameras and get it done.
["ID302b29fbf020a86b"] = "상점으로 들어가면 뭘 해야겠어? 보석들을 챙기는 일이지!", --Get into the store, you know what to do! Let's get those jewels.
["ID0260e6ecb4b9c67b"] = "진열장을 찾아 부수고 보석들을 쓸어담아.", --Look for the cases, break them and bag the jewels.
