["IDc38a6c9ebe6738ce"] = "잠깐 얘들아, 나 국제통용화학물질번호를 잘못 읽은거 같아. ...얘들아?", --Wait guys, I think I'm confusing these CAS registry numbers. ...guys?
["ID29b919c7e70f9475"] = "젠장, 보아하니 경찰들이 여기서 잠복하고 있었나봐. 서둘러!", --Damn, looks like the cops had been staking the place. Move it!
["IDbba02c2dc4b75e1a"] = "아 이런, 경찰회선이 요란치고 있어. 아마도 경찰들이 여기를 감시하고 있었나봐.", --Ah hell. Heat is on the way. Guess the cops were watching the place.
["IDe49c79b9bfabaaca"] = "낭비할 시간 없어. 안으로 들어가!", --No time to waste. Get in there!
["ID4944fdd77cd51b1d"] = "혹시 재료가 부족해? 만약 남아서 조금 더 제조하고 싶으면, 공중으로 물자를 너희에게 공급할 수 있어... 너희는 헬리콥터에 신호만 보내면 돼. 아니면 지금 도망쳐도 돼. 너희들이 선택해.", --Running low on ingredients? If you want to stay and cook a little more, there's a supply drop waiting in the wings for you... Just signal the helicopter. Or you can bail now. Your choice.
["ID747d5ea897be761f"] = "재료가 얼마 안남았을거야. 너희가 더 원한다면, 조명탄을 이용해서 헬리콥터에 신호를 줘. 조종사가 너희가 필요한 재료를 줄거야. 아니면 지금 거기서 나와도 돼. 너희가 선택해.", --There are only a few ingredients left. You want more, just use a flare to signal the helicopter. He's got what you need for cooking more. Or you can bug out now. Up to you.
["ID221495efcbfa8f90"] = "거기에 재료가 다 떨어졌을거야. 만약 재료가 더 필요하다면, 조명탄으로 헬리콥터에 신호를 줘. 우리 조종사가 항시 대기중이니까, 금방 도착할거야. 아니면 그냥 튀던지. 너희가 선택해.", --This place is running low on supplies. If you wanna go for more ingredients, signal the chopper with a flare. This pilot's on the clock, so make it worth while. Or you can bounce. Your call.
["ID6cbf9aad9f1da455"] = "위치 선정하나 좋군. 이제 기다려 봐.", --Good spot. Now we wait.
["ID46efae10baf2ef0f"] = "좋아, 이제 조종사를 기다려.", --OK, now wait for the pilot.
["ID38a678c57e36003c"] = "됐다. 이제 조종사가 응답할 때까지 기다려.", --That's it. Now wait for the pilot to signal in.
["IDdbf2687fbfaf36c0"] = "물자가 도착했어. 가지고 와서 제조실 안에 배치해.", --There's the drop. Snatch it and place it by the lab.
["ID293ca5444bbed9a3"] = "재료가 도착했어. 회수해와! 집 안에다가 확보하도록 해.", --There're the ingredients. Grab 'em! Secure them in the house.
["ID9ef72bfade8d2f1d"] = "조종사가 물자를 떨어트렸어. 집 안으로 가지고 와.", --Pilot dropped the supplies. Get them into the house.
["IDbf3566d39db71eab"] = "터트리지 말고 제조하라고, 친구들.", --Be careful with the cooking, gentlemen.
["IDd44358d7cb027dfe"] = "잘했어. 이제 이 집만 태워먹지 말자고, 얘들아.", --Alright. Don't burn the place down, guys.
["ID11dab1a8a9ad38e9"] = "좋아, 이제 상품을 더 만들어 보자. 그러니 제발 불만 지르지마.", --Great. Let's cook a little more product. Just don't set anything on fire.
["ID4c74801676ebe912"] = "어떻게 할지 알지? 재료를 던져줄 헬리콥터를 호출하면 돼. 아니면 거기를 뜨던지, 너희가 결정해.", --You know the deal: signal the helicopter to catch more ingredients. Or leave the place, up to you.
["IDccc7105194c7a01f"] = "어떻게 하는지는 알고 있겠지. 헬리콥터를 호출해서, 재료를 더 받던지, 아니면 도망치던지. 너희가 선택해.", --You know what to do. Signal the chopper, and we'll drop off more ingredients. Or bail. Your choice.
["IDf457bbeaa8fe32ff"] = "또 재료가 부족한거야? 문제없어, 헬리콥터한테 더 달라고 호출해. 아니면 거기서 나오던지. 너희가 결정해.", --Out of ingredients again? No problem, signal the chopper for more. Or get out of there. Your call.
["ID17bb382833464305"] = "재료를 가지고 집안으로 가지고 와.", --Grab the raw materials and get them in the house.
["ID1e296596803773d8"] = "얘들아, 가방을 들고 제조실 안에 던져넣어.", --Gang, snatch the bag and dump it by the methlab.
["IDfd887d41d8685729"] = "지금 밖에 재료가 나뒹굴고있어, 제군들. 제조실 안에다 확보하도록 해.", --There's supplies waiting for you, gentlemen. Secure 'em by the lab.
["ID1778d8a5bbb13cbf"] = "더 이상 이 제조실을 사용할 수 없어. 완전히 불타버렸어.", --We can't use the lab anymore, it's gone
["IDbe3da7ba437069eb"] = "", --This is a simple job, but that doesn't mean it will be easy. We're going to head out to the forest. You remember the place. We did some work for Hector out there. Anyway, I scoped the place out and it is still intact. So, we're headed there to cook up as much meth as we can. You can stay as long as you want. If you run out of supplies, I'll get more flown in. Should be easy money.
["IDe974c74dc3c2a216"] = "", --You guys remember that sketchy old house out in the forest? Where Hector's guys were cooking up meth? Well, we're headed back there. 
["IDd333cd64a156085f"] = "", --We're headed back to cook in the meth lab in the forest. None of Hector's shit this time. This is just for profit.
["ID89e847983fe6d260"] = "", --Well, in the annals of criminal cock-ups, that ranks high. I can hear the cops laughing from here. Better luck next time.
["IDf0176bb64ebef07a"] = "", --Well, you got a decent amount. Just about covers the gas money. Maybe next time we can push it further.
["ID451c399c75fc27c5"] = "", --Nice haul! This will bring in a nice chunk of change. Good job!
["IDb41711fb84fff93c"] = "", --Hot damn! You guys did great! Enjoy your PAYDAY - you deserve it.
