["ID491d4611cd11cf9b"] = "울프, 아까 네가 불도저에 한 짓 말이야... 너 상담 좀 받아봐야 할거같다, 친구.", --Wolf, what you did with that Bulldozer back there was a bit... I think you need help, mate.
