["ID5ba180b8f0e59c41"] = "페이저 담당 요원이 좀 멍청하긴 하지만, 또 한번 페이저에 응답하게 되면, 녀석도 더 이상 속지 않을꺼야.", --That Control-Guy doesn't seem to be the brightest tool in the shed, but next time even he will understand something's wrong.
["IDe0bd4efcab424f2d"] = "저 쓰레기통이면 될거야.", --That dumpster should do the trick.
