["IDfafb456c228a5364"] = "별로 어렵지도 않군. 좋아, 드릴을 설치해서 저 금고를 열자.", --That was easy. Okay, deploy your drill and get that safe open.
["ID7b619332efac3ae9"] = "몰래몰래 움직이는거 참 잘하는데, 달라스. 감명깊은데.", --That was some damn good sneaking, Dallas. I am impressed.
["IDc9f6f08fa39be2ff"] = "그럴필요는 없었잖아, 달라스... 카메라를 부수면 경비들이 가만히 있지는 않는다고.", --That was unnecesssary, Dallas... Destroying cameras will not go unnoticed.
["IDbaf6742086954a38"] = "잘했어! 이제 가자! 아직도 실력 살아있구나, 달라스!", --That's it! Time to go! You still got it, Dallas!
["ID8c2a6e1557a0fdc2"] = "다 됐다, 베인. 모든 기록을 삭제했어.", --That's it, Bain. All the records have been deleted.
["IDe2701ae6e1fcfabb"] = "좋아, 해냈군! 코카인을 차에 넣고 어서 가자고.", --That's it, you made it! Throw the coke in the van and let's go.
