["IDb1baff7285aa3c17"] = "정문으로 가는건 자살행위야. 옆으로 돌아서 가자고. 마스크를 쓰고 철조망이나 잘라봐.", --The main entrance would be suicide. We're sneaking in from the side instead. Put on your mask and cut open that fence.
