["IDf48ed86a2507a706"] = "우와, 이거 참 지저분한 광경이군. 저 시체들을 숨기자.", --Well, that's quite a mess all right. Now get these bodies out of sight.
["IDeeb36d1c00f5fb5a"] = "음, 내가 기억했던것 보다 훨씬 어려운데.", --Well, this was harder than I remembered it to be.
["IDc453671021134045"] = "이야, 이게 뭐지? 저게 우리가 찾은 컴퓨터인거 같은데. 근처에 있는거 같아.", --Well, what do we have here? That should be the computer. I think it's close by.
["ID6dbc541dc4621315"] = "나이트클럽에 도착했어. 솜씨를 보여줄 시간이야. 일단 재미보기 전에 주변을 정찰해보자고. 먼저 잘 살펴보고 침착하게 행동해.", --We're at the night club. Time to get your dance-on. Start by ''casing'' the place before the fun begins. Take a look around first and keep things casual.
["IDa8882c91dae8d25c"] = "차분하고 조용하게 진행하자고. 우리가 노리는 컴퓨터는 2층에 있어.", --We're doing this nice and quiet. The computer we're looking for should be located on the second floor. 
["IDaf72b3d20b01868c"] = "도착했어. 안에 들어가서 접속 코드를 찾아와.", --We're here. Get inside and get your hands on the access codes.
