["ID82bb19876a5d547c"] = "분명 우리가 써먹거나 팔만한 좋은 물건이 넘쳐날테니까, 가져갈만한 물건이 있는지 잘 살펴보라고.There's got to be lot's of good stuff we can use or sell around here, so keep your eyes peeled for anything that might be good to take along.", --There's got to be lot's of good stuff we can use or sell around here, so keep your eyes peeled for anything that might be good to take along.
